-- Rank Group in Talks to Buy Gala Coral’s Casinos, Times Says
-- B y   A n n e - S y l v a i n e   C h a s s a n y
-- 2012-01-29T13:04:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-29/rank-group-in-talks-to-buy-gala-coral-s-casino-chain-times-says.html
Rank Group Plc (RNK) , which has the
Grosvenor casinos in the U.K., is in talks to buy the casino
unit of Gala Coral Group Ltd., the British gaming company run by
creditors led by Apollo Global Management LLC, the Sunday Times
said, without citing anyone.  Rank’s deal would value the Gala’s 24 gaming centers at as
much as 250 million pounds ($393 million), according to the
newspaper.  Sarah Mercer, a spokeswoman for Gala Coral’s casino unit,
couldn’t be reached immediately. A spokesman for Rank couldn’t
be reached immediately.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anne-Sylvaine Chassany in London at 
 achassany@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
